  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK459">
<l>maṉanalatti ṉāku maṟumaimaṟ ṟaḵtu </l>
<l>miṉanalatti ṉēmāp puṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Future bliss is (the result) of goodness of mind and even this acquires strength from the society of the good.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
